  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个用户注册流程图，从感谢注册页面开始，然后分两条路走：一条是验证邮箱后进入待审批，另一条是直接跳到待确认状态。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "thanksSigningUp",
        "thanksVerifying",
        "pendingApproval",
        "pendingConfirmation"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，起点是/enrollment/thanks-for-signing-up。那两条分支分别是：1）验证后去pending-approval，2）直接去pending-confirmation？这两条分支都从起点出发吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "thanksSigningUp",
        "thanksVerifying",
        "pendingApproval",
        "pendingConfirmation"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，起点同时连到验证感谢页和待确认页。然后验证感谢页再连到待审批。另外，待确认页也能回到验证感谢页，形成一个小循环。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "thanksSigningUp",
        "thanksVerifying",
        "pendingConfirmation",
        "pendingApproval"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把四个节点建出来：thanks-for-signing-up、thanks-for-verifying、pending-approval、pending-confirmation。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "thanksSigningUp",
        "thanksVerifying",
        "pendingApproval",
        "pendingConfirmation"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "连线我这样做：起点→验证感谢，起点→待确认，验证感谢→待审批。待确认回到验证感谢这条线，是双向的还是单向的？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "thanksSigningUp",
        "thanksVerifying",
        "pendingConfirmation",
        "pendingApproval"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "待确认到验证感谢是单向的，用户确认后需要重新验证。不是双向循环。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "pendingConfirmation",
        "thanksVerifying"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已调整，待确认单向指向验证感谢。现在四条线都连好了：起点分叉到验证和待确认，验证再到审批，待确认可返回验证。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "thanksSigningUp",
        "thanksVerifying",
        "pendingApproval",
        "pendingConfirmation"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，这样流程就完整了。用户注册后要么直接待确认，要么验证后待审批，待确认的用户还能回头再验证。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "thanksSigningUp",
        "thanksVerifying",
        "pendingApproval",
        "pendingConfirmation"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    }
